init_text: You're Barack Obama. 4 years into your retirement, you awake to find a letter with no return address on your bedside table. It reads "I hope you've had a chance to relax Barack...but pack your bags and call the number below. It's time to start the real job." Signed simply, "JFK."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You know what you have to do.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You arrive at the location and see a man in a black suit, white shirt, and black tie.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You arrive at a facility and are greeted by a man in a white coat.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You wake up in a white room with a white bed.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You check the windows and they are barred.
